marked: The aim of the present investigation was to assess the correlation between the score on a word list learning task and brain perfusion measured by single-photon emission computed tomography (SPECT) using a voxel-based analysis, in a consecutive series of patients with very mild AD
with and without controlling for the severity of global cognitive impairment.
